23:37.551 --> 23:39.785
No.
We don't really get along.

23:40.622 --> 23:43.289
Where were you this morning
around 10:00 a.m.?

23:44.826 --> 23:47.026
Uh, here.

23:47.028 --> 23:48.694
Can anyone verify that?

23:48.696 --> 23:51.163
She can.
She was with me.

23:51.165 --> 23:56.302
♪♪

23:56.304 --> 23:58.237
We -- We --
We slept in.

23:58.239 --> 24:04.710
♪♪

24:04.712 --> 24:07.313
Give us a call
if your uncle contacts you.

24:07.315 --> 24:09.849
Oh. He won't.

24:09.851 --> 24:11.050
Why would he?

24:11.052 --> 24:18.123
♪♪

24:18.125 --> 24:25.331
♪♪

24:25.333 --> 24:32.404
♪♪

24:32.406 --> 24:34.006
[ Animal grunts ]

24:34.008 --> 24:36.742
[ Sirens wailing in distance ]

24:36.744 --> 24:39.011
Okay.

24:39.013 --> 24:40.812
Let's go.

24:40.814 --> 24:44.750
♪♪

24:44.752 --> 24:47.019
[ Animals bleating ]

24:47.021 --> 24:54.360
♪♪

24:54.362 --> 25:01.901
♪♪

25:01.903 --> 25:03.369
Clear.

25:03.371 --> 25:12.912
♪♪

25:12.914 --> 25:22.254
♪♪

25:22.256 --> 25:25.057
Oh, shit.

25:25.059 --> 25:27.527
They're coming this way.

25:27.529 --> 25:28.994
I think they found us.

25:28.996 --> 25:30.396
Sounds like
a lot of cops.

25:30.398 --> 25:32.331
There's gonna be
a lot more soon.

25:32.333 --> 25:34.266
What are we gonna do?

25:34.268 --> 25:37.202
Oh, shit.
Oh, God.

25:37.204 --> 25:38.604
This is on me.

25:38.606 --> 25:40.940
It's on me.
I trusted J.

25:40.942 --> 25:42.408
We all did.

25:42.410 --> 25:43.543
God damn it.

25:43.545 --> 25:45.411
Yeah, we did.
I trusted him.

25:45.413 --> 25:47.346
I'll kill him.
I'll kill him.

25:47.348 --> 25:48.880
What do we got?

25:48.882 --> 25:51.083
We got three handguns,
the sheriff's shotgun,

25:51.085 --> 25:52.351
and that .22.

25:52.353 --> 25:54.320
[ Wailing continues ]

25:57.024 --> 25:58.490
Hey.

25:58.492 --> 25:59.725
Look at me.

26:01.562 --> 26:03.429
Get your shit together.

26:03.431 --> 26:09.836
♪♪

26:19.180 --> 26:23.048
So, did Smurf throw out
all my shit?

26:23.050 --> 26:25.284
Yeah.
Last year.

26:30.658 --> 26:33.559
[ Groans softly,
sniffs ]

26:36.063 --> 26:38.864
It's crazy, right?

26:38.866 --> 26:40.900
Was that guy you broke in with
the dad?

26:48.342 --> 26:49.876
Is Baz the dad?

26:51.745 --> 26:52.712
Maybe.

26:55.549 --> 26:57.416
I don't know
who the dad is.

27:05.092 --> 27:06.759
It's a boy.

27:12.366 --> 27:14.567
Smurf said it's time
for you to come out.

27:22.043 --> 27:24.510
[ Exhales sharply ]

27:24.512 --> 27:26.245
There's no car.

27:26.247 --> 27:27.446
[ Exhales sharply ]

27:27.448 --> 27:28.915
But there's a KTM.

27:31.185 --> 27:32.852
There's just one?

27:32.854 --> 27:34.587
Just the one.

27:34.922 --> 27:37.389
Damn.

27:37.391 --> 27:38.991
[ Groaning ] Okay.

27:42.263 --> 27:43.896
Um...

27:48.202 --> 27:51.003
Well...

27:51.005 --> 27:53.605
Uh, Pope?

27:53.607 --> 27:56.876
What are we gonna do, Pope?
You two take it.

27:56.878 --> 27:58.610
There's no way.

27:58.612 --> 28:00.012
Not happening, Pope.

28:00.014 --> 28:03.749
I'll draw fire out the front.
You go out the back.

28:03.751 --> 28:05.817
We're gonna leave you here?
No.
I'm not doing that.

28:05.819 --> 28:07.753
That's the plan.
No, it's not.
It's not happening.

28:07.755 --> 28:10.622
You don't have a choice.
There's gonna be a helicopter
here before you know it.

28:10.624 --> 28:13.559
You're not gonna be able
to get out. You gotta go now.
Craig.

28:13.561 --> 28:14.694
We're gonna finish
this together.

28:14.696 --> 28:16.762
No.
This is how it goes.

28:16.764 --> 28:18.898
This is how it has to be.
There's another way to do this.

28:18.900 --> 28:19.899
There's gotta be
another way.

28:19.901 --> 28:22.234
You take the Colt
and the .22.

28:22.236 --> 28:23.503
Gimme your guns.

28:23.505 --> 28:25.237
No.
No.

28:25.239 --> 28:27.373
[ Sirens wailing ]

28:27.375 --> 28:28.774
Give me the --

28:28.776 --> 28:30.109
No, Pope.

28:30.111 --> 28:31.577
Give it to me.

28:35.182 --> 28:37.449
We're not going.

28:37.451 --> 28:39.585
Hey.

28:39.587 --> 28:42.355
Hey, we're gonna be okay.
I'm gonna be alright.

28:44.392 --> 28:47.059
Yeah.

28:47.061 --> 28:48.594
Go.

28:51.999 --> 28:53.599
I'll come find you.

28:53.601 --> 28:55.467
[ Wailing continues ]

28:55.469 --> 29:02.208
♪♪

29:02.210 --> 29:09.081
♪♪

29:09.083 --> 29:11.216
Alright.

29:11.218 --> 29:12.218
Later.

29:12.220 --> 29:19.291
♪♪

29:19.293 --> 29:26.432
♪♪

29:26.434 --> 29:27.934
[ Gun cocks ]

29:35.610 --> 29:38.276
What was that?

29:38.278 --> 29:39.345
What?

29:39.347 --> 29:40.546
The police.

29:40.548 --> 29:42.281
Why'd you make me
lie to them?

29:44.352 --> 29:45.884
Did you know?

29:45.886 --> 29:47.753
Is that why you had me
alter those trust documents?

29:47.755 --> 29:49.355
No.

29:53.161 --> 29:55.227
Are they gonna
come after us?

29:55.229 --> 29:56.695
Your -- Your uncles?

29:56.697 --> 29:57.630
No.

29:57.632 --> 29:59.031
You can't know that.

29:59.033 --> 30:00.566
Penny --
You said Pope was dangerous.

30:00.568 --> 30:02.034
You said that they were
all dangerous.

30:02.036 --> 30:04.570
It's fine.
They're not gonna get far.

30:04.572 --> 30:06.104
I handled it.

30:06.106 --> 30:06.973
I discovered what
they were planning

30:06.975 --> 30:08.507
and I called the police.

30:08.509 --> 30:10.309
So, you<i> did</i> know
what was gonna happen?

30:11.712 --> 30:14.112
Can you just trust me?

30:14.114 --> 30:15.748
Please?

30:21.522 --> 30:23.589
I think...

30:23.591 --> 30:25.992
I think maybe you should
go without me.

30:28.462 --> 30:34.533
♪♪

30:34.535 --> 30:35.601
No.

30:35.603 --> 30:36.869
No, no, no.
It's fine.

30:36.871 --> 30:38.270
No, it's not.
It is.

30:38.272 --> 30:39.672
It's not fine.

30:39.674 --> 30:49.548
♪♪

30:49.550 --> 30:51.417
Do you love me?
Yeah.

30:51.419 --> 30:53.886
Of course.

30:53.888 --> 30:56.622
I just...

30:56.624 --> 30:59.225
I don't think
I should go.

30:59.227 --> 31:05.297
♪♪

31:05.299 --> 31:11.570
♪♪

31:11.572 --> 31:12.971
[ Sighs ]

31:12.973 --> 31:22.114
♪♪

31:22.116 --> 31:24.650
Will you, um...

31:24.652 --> 31:28.454
Will you at least wait with me
until I have to leave?

31:28.456 --> 31:29.989
Of course.

31:32.860 --> 31:34.360
Okay.

31:36.530 --> 31:38.264
[ Water splashing ]

31:47.742 --> 31:51.477
Are you feeling better?

31:51.479 --> 31:53.746
Yeah.

31:53.748 --> 31:55.147
Thank you.

31:55.149 --> 31:57.883
What was I
supposed to do?

31:57.885 --> 32:01.287
Have you incarcerated
for grand larceny?

32:01.289 --> 32:03.489
Make you have that baby
in jail?

32:14.435 --> 32:15.735
Hey, Craig.

32:18.306 --> 32:20.506
You can't
have your room back.

32:21.509 --> 32:23.375
Smurf: Aww, baby.

32:23.377 --> 32:25.911
Julia's not staying.

32:25.913 --> 32:27.914
She's a big girl.

32:29.317 --> 32:32.384
She likes
to do things...

32:32.386 --> 32:33.786
her own way.

32:35.189 --> 32:37.823
Come on.
Don't leave your brother alone.

32:40.328 --> 32:42.028
So...

32:50.338 --> 32:51.938
Good luck.

32:54.408 --> 33:00.078
♪♪

33:00.080 --> 33:02.281
-Smurf, I --
-She needs help.

33:04.218 --> 33:06.819
Pope: So does the baby.

33:06.821 --> 33:09.221
Andrew, it's okay.

33:09.223 --> 33:11.357
Rehab.

33:11.359 --> 33:14.527
Yeah, 'cause that worked
so well last time.

33:16.764 --> 33:19.097
I'll do it.

33:19.099 --> 33:20.967
I will.
I'll -- I'll make it work.

33:20.969 --> 33:22.568
For the baby.
I will.

33:25.039 --> 33:26.305
Please.

33:26.307 --> 33:32.645
♪♪

33:32.647 --> 33:34.280
Please.

33:37.918 --> 33:40.386
I'll make some calls.

33:40.388 --> 33:49.461
♪♪

33:49.463 --> 33:58.404
♪♪

33:58.406 --> 34:07.479
♪♪

34:07.481 --> 34:16.555
♪♪

34:16.557 --> 34:18.424
[ Ice cubes rattling ]

34:18.426 --> 34:24.096
♪♪

34:24.098 --> 34:29.968
♪♪

34:29.970 --> 34:32.205
Penny:
I really am sorry, J.

34:33.842 --> 34:35.341
Me too.

34:37.045 --> 34:38.411
I just --

34:40.715 --> 34:43.382
I got swept up.

34:43.384 --> 34:46.852
I was asking a lot
of you.

34:46.854 --> 34:50.456
I won't tell anyone,
you know.

34:50.458 --> 34:51.523
I know.

34:51.525 --> 34:58.797
♪♪

34:58.799 --> 35:06.072
♪♪

35:06.074 --> 35:07.907
[ Door opens ]

35:09.610 --> 35:12.144
Man: Watch out!
Shots fired!

35:12.146 --> 35:13.612
[ Grunts ]

35:13.614 --> 35:15.214
[ Men grunting ]

35:18.152 --> 35:20.018
[ Gunshots ]

35:20.020 --> 35:25.824
♪♪

35:25.826 --> 35:27.626
Get on the ground!

35:27.628 --> 35:32.831
♪♪

35:32.833 --> 35:37.970
♪♪

35:37.972 --> 35:40.172
[ Sirens wailing ]

35:40.174 --> 35:47.713
♪♪

35:47.715 --> 35:55.387
♪♪

35:55.389 --> 36:03.029
♪♪

36:10.104 --> 36:12.405
[ Tires screech ]

36:23.384 --> 36:24.250
[ Gun clatters ]

36:24.252 --> 36:28.054
[ Sirens wailing in distance ]

36:28.056 --> 36:36.395
♪♪

36:36.397 --> 36:44.803
♪♪

36:44.805 --> 36:46.272
Get out.

36:48.076 --> 36:51.209
I said get out!

36:51.211 --> 36:52.811
Hey!

36:52.813 --> 36:59.685
♪♪

36:59.687 --> 37:02.220
You're just gonna
leave me out here?

37:02.222 --> 37:07.025
♪♪

37:07.027 --> 37:08.895
[ Tires screech ]

37:08.897 --> 37:16.302
♪♪

37:16.304 --> 37:18.837
You hit?
Yeah, it's fine, it's fine.

37:18.839 --> 37:21.574
We need cash and a first-aid kit
or something, alright?

37:26.247 --> 37:27.846
Are you ready?

37:27.848 --> 37:36.789
♪♪

37:36.791 --> 37:38.657
Money in the register.
Now.

37:38.659 --> 37:40.326
What are you waiting for?
Move!
Let's go. Come on.

37:40.328 --> 37:41.794
[ Cash register beeping ]

37:41.796 --> 37:43.462
Craig: You got
a first-aid kit?

37:43.464 --> 37:45.597
Do you have a first-aid kit?
Gauze and shit?

37:45.599 --> 37:46.732
We need that, too.
Put it in the bag.

37:46.734 --> 37:48.200
Let's go.
How about that truck outside?

37:48.202 --> 37:49.468
Is that yours?
The Dodge?

37:49.470 --> 37:51.003
Is that your truck?!
Yes.

37:51.005 --> 37:52.471
I need the keys to that, too.
Put them in the bag.

37:52.473 --> 37:53.672
-Come on!
-Come on. Let's go.

37:53.674 --> 37:55.273
[ Gunshots ]
Ah!

37:55.275 --> 37:56.675
[ Groaning ]

37:56.677 --> 37:58.811
Man: No! No, no!

37:58.813 --> 38:01.013
No! Please!
Please!

38:01.015 --> 38:02.448
Please.

38:04.285 --> 38:05.518
Please.

38:06.154 --> 38:07.687
Please.

38:09.290 --> 38:11.157
Please.

38:11.159 --> 38:15.627
♪♪

38:15.629 --> 38:17.095
[ Groans ]

38:17.097 --> 38:26.038
♪♪

38:26.040 --> 38:28.174
[ Tires screech ]

38:28.176 --> 38:35.314
♪♪

38:46.861 --> 38:54.733
♪♪

38:54.735 --> 38:57.003
[ Tires screech ]

38:57.005 --> 39:05.544
♪♪

39:05.546 --> 39:14.286
♪♪

39:14.288 --> 39:23.029
♪♪

39:23.031 --> 39:31.970
♪♪

39:31.972 --> 39:40.512
♪♪

39:40.514 --> 39:49.255
♪♪

39:49.257 --> 39:57.796
♪♪

39:57.798 --> 40:00.266
[ Breathing heavily ]

40:00.268 --> 40:08.540
♪♪

40:08.542 --> 40:17.015
♪♪

40:17.017 --> 40:25.091
♪♪

40:25.093 --> 40:27.226
[ Screaming ]

40:27.228 --> 40:35.568
♪♪

40:35.570 --> 40:37.904
[ Glass breaking ]

40:37.906 --> 40:46.378
♪♪

40:46.380 --> 40:55.121
♪♪

40:55.123 --> 41:03.595
♪♪

41:03.597 --> 41:05.464
[ Grunts ]

41:05.466 --> 41:14.072
♪♪

41:14.074 --> 41:22.681
♪♪

41:22.683 --> 41:24.616
[ Glass shattering ]

41:24.618 --> 41:31.757
♪♪

41:31.759 --> 41:39.165
♪♪

41:39.167 --> 41:46.305
♪♪

41:46.307 --> 41:47.974
[ Shouts ]

41:47.976 --> 41:56.715
♪♪

41:56.717 --> 42:05.457
♪♪

42:05.459 --> 42:14.100
♪♪

42:17.338 --> 42:23.909
♪♪

42:23.911 --> 42:30.115
♪♪

42:30.117 --> 42:32.351
What do you think
about Josh?

42:35.256 --> 42:36.856
J for short.

42:39.393 --> 42:41.227
It's good.

42:43.597 --> 42:45.665
I can't wait
to meet him.

42:47.068 --> 42:48.701
You want to feel?

42:51.739 --> 42:52.672
Yeah?

42:52.674 --> 42:59.011
♪♪

42:59.013 --> 43:00.412
When's he due?

43:00.414 --> 43:01.947
About two months.

43:01.949 --> 43:06.886
♪♪

43:06.888 --> 43:09.221
I missed you so much.

43:09.223 --> 43:17.897
♪♪

43:17.899 --> 43:26.838
♪♪

43:26.840 --> 43:35.514
♪♪

43:35.516 --> 43:38.584
[ Breathing heavily ]

43:38.586 --> 43:40.652
Yeah.

43:40.654 --> 43:43.923
That's good.
You're awake.

43:43.925 --> 43:45.591
Pope --
No.

43:45.593 --> 43:48.394
I can't listen to
any more lies, J.

43:48.396 --> 43:49.995
No, no, no.

43:49.997 --> 43:52.732
We trusted you.

43:52.734 --> 43:55.801
We made you
part of the family.

43:55.803 --> 43:58.938
We brought you in
and we trusted you!

44:00.408 --> 44:03.542
And you set us up
to die!

44:03.544 --> 44:05.444
My brothers!

44:06.948 --> 44:08.614
To die!

44:11.953 --> 44:16.622
You think you're so smart.
Why did you come back here, J?

44:16.624 --> 44:18.558
To set your alibi
when the cops show up?

44:18.560 --> 44:21.026
No, no, Pope, I had heat.
I had heat.

44:21.028 --> 44:22.695
I was calling
to tell you.

44:26.100 --> 44:27.366
You kill this girl?

44:27.368 --> 44:28.834
I had to, man.

44:28.836 --> 44:30.702
She -- She was gonna
call the cops,

44:30.704 --> 44:31.904
and I was gonna
come and find you --

44:31.906 --> 44:33.606
No more lies!

44:36.644 --> 44:39.011
It didn't
have to be this way.

44:42.784 --> 44:44.516
But you are
who you are!

44:44.518 --> 44:47.719
You did what you did!

44:47.721 --> 44:50.990
So you know
what happens next.

44:50.992 --> 44:54.526
You deserved it.

44:54.528 --> 44:56.595
All of you.

44:56.597 --> 44:58.330
For what you did
to my mom.

44:58.332 --> 44:59.866
You deserved it.

45:01.535 --> 45:03.469
You deserved it!

45:03.471 --> 45:08.808
♪♪

45:08.810 --> 45:10.676
You could've saved her.

45:10.678 --> 45:12.878
You could've saved her,
but you didn't.

45:12.880 --> 45:22.488
♪♪

45:22.490 --> 45:24.356
Julia:
Ready to be an uncle?

45:24.358 --> 45:28.760
♪♪

45:28.762 --> 45:30.830
[ Water bubbling ]

45:30.832 --> 45:36.502
♪♪

45:36.504 --> 45:39.438
[ Gearshift clicks,
engine shuts off ]

45:39.440 --> 45:40.873
Smurf: We're here.

45:45.046 --> 45:46.378
Pope: This is rehab?

45:46.380 --> 45:48.247
No. It's not.

45:48.249 --> 45:51.250
Rehab.
For you?

45:51.252 --> 45:53.719
Again?

45:53.721 --> 45:56.522
Waste of money.

45:56.524 --> 45:58.391
Got something to say,
Andrew?

46:01.062 --> 46:02.594
Say it.

46:02.596 --> 46:10.736
♪♪

46:10.738 --> 46:12.638
Let's try this again.

46:17.411 --> 46:19.278
Go on, baby.

46:19.280 --> 46:20.946
Take it.

46:20.948 --> 46:23.683
This is the last bit of cash
that you and that little bastard

46:23.685 --> 46:25.685
are ever gonna get
from me.

46:29.757 --> 46:31.757
Andrew, come with us.
I-I --

46:31.759 --> 46:33.492
Please. You need to get away
from her right now.

46:33.494 --> 46:34.826
Please.
Just come with us.

46:34.828 --> 46:37.162
Get out of my car now.

46:37.164 --> 46:42.568
♪♪

46:42.570 --> 46:44.236
Andrew, please.

46:44.238 --> 46:46.038
Oh, you wanna go?

46:46.040 --> 46:47.673
Go.

46:50.644 --> 46:54.580
Baby, you know there's
no turning back, though.

46:54.582 --> 46:56.182
Once you're out,
you're out.

46:59.453 --> 47:00.887
Andrew, please.

47:05.393 --> 47:06.792
Aah!

47:06.794 --> 47:09.661
She begged me. She begged me.
She begged me.

47:09.663 --> 47:17.669
♪♪

47:17.671 --> 47:20.005
Andrew, please,
we need you.

47:20.007 --> 47:21.707
Please.

47:25.479 --> 47:26.879
Come on, baby.

47:28.882 --> 47:30.750
Come sit up front
with me.

47:30.752 --> 47:38.490
♪♪

47:38.492 --> 47:46.232
♪♪

47:46.234 --> 47:47.433
Andrew.

47:47.435 --> 47:56.108
♪♪

47:56.110 --> 47:57.577
My baby boy.

47:57.579 --> 48:04.450
♪♪

48:04.452 --> 48:11.056
♪♪

48:11.058 --> 48:13.125
[ Sobbing ]

48:13.127 --> 48:20.132
♪♪

48:20.134 --> 48:27.139
♪♪

48:27.141 --> 48:29.074
[ Screams ]

48:29.076 --> 48:38.350
♪♪

48:38.352 --> 48:40.352
[ Gasps, coughing ]

48:40.354 --> 48:46.291
♪♪

48:46.293 --> 48:52.031
♪♪

48:52.033 --> 48:54.033
[ Coughing ]

48:58.906 --> 49:00.973
[ Gasping ]

49:03.177 --> 49:06.145
She wanted me to be stronger
than I was.

49:09.783 --> 49:13.853
She wanted me to pretend
I was normal,

49:13.855 --> 49:16.188
and I wasn't normal.

49:16.190 --> 49:19.592
Your mother was the strong one.
I was the weak one!

49:22.596 --> 49:25.531
She loved you.

49:25.533 --> 49:26.798
She always loved you.

49:26.800 --> 49:29.801
She never stopped.
She loved all of you.

49:30.271 --> 49:33.039
And you didn't do shit
for her.

49:34.608 --> 49:36.342
Nothing.
[ Coughs ]

49:39.413 --> 49:41.146
All of them.

